{"tid":2514254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ITZY新歌評價兩極！全靠禮志拯救超醜「青蛙舞」","createTime":"2021-05-03T06:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T06:57:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72cf5205c5c6a52435e38b458683dad6d8f894dc","tid":2514254,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2021/05/03/phpwfzxHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2FphpwfzxHC.jpg&h=fcda8ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓女團ITZY的新歌《Mafia In The Morning》評價兩極。（翻攝自IG <a href=\"http://itzy.all.in.us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fitzy.all.in.us&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=300a004d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">itzy.all.in.us</a>）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕JYP娛樂旗下人氣女團ITZY最近發行新歌《Mafia In The Morning》成為網友話題中心，不過許多人對於她們的歌曲評價兩極，宣傳期的服裝造型也引起爭議，讓網友感到相當不解，除此之外，也有網友在韓國論壇上提出自己對於新歌舞蹈的看法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2021/05/03/phpXxrYEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2FphpXxrYEG.jpg&h=e2a44ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nITZY隊長禮志在MV中的舞步，被人吐槽很像青蛙。（翻攝自YouTube JYP Entertainment）<br />\n<br />\n近日韓國論壇上出現一篇以「ITZY新歌中評價兩極的舞蹈」為題的文章，該網友貼出隊長禮志在MV中蹲下開腿跳舞的截圖，並稱禮志是「越看越有感覺」，且舞步很有嘻哈風格，給出不錯的評價，卻意外引起網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n有網友在留言區毒舌吐槽這個舞步根本就是「很醜的青蛙姿勢」，認為這樣的舞蹈根本不適合她們，只因為是禮志所以才好看，更稱直呼：「禮志救了這編舞。」不過也有網友持相反意見，紛紛稱讚：「我覺得超帥欸！」、「這個片段我至少看了30分鐘。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ysomCGaZLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_ysomCGaZLw&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=0797ae7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ysomCGaZLw</a>"},{"pid":"6f9ec226f62f4c821a2aa82422e376801d1d40b5","tid":2514254,"uid":80047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"睇完showcase之後無聽/睇過首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e672265f9b34c3d609e7d21c9bbe5735220257be","tid":2514254,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:54:29.000Z","msg":"請你唔好背叛TWICE<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b77647b436af0ca1afb8acb64c22c2b9532f58","tid":2514254,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e672265f9b34c3d609e7d21c9bbe5735220257be","tid":2514254,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:54:29.000Z","msg":"請你唔好背叛TWICE<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"談何背叛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}